OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first, with a few
OL,6,Foutbreaks of light rain in the
OL,7,Fmorning, mostly in the north. However,
OL,8,Fthis will clear and skies will
OL,9,Fbrighten through the afternoon with
OL,10,Fsome warm sunny spells developing in
OL,11,Fpretty light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry and largely clear night
OL,14,Fto come with a light southerly wind.
OL,15,FStaying very mild overnight with some
OL,16,Fplaces staying in the mid-teens.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
