OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA bright start to the day and
OL,6,Fstaying dry throughout. High cloud
OL,7,Fspilling in through the afternoon, but
OL,8,Ftemperatures continue to rise above
OL,9,Fthe May average in the strong sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FVery
OL,12,Fwarm or hot over the Bank Holiday
OL,13,Fweekend with plenty of sunshine and
OL,14,Flight winds. Sunshine may turn hazy at
OL,15,Ftimes with some patchy cloud possible
OL,16,Fbriefly on Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
